{"type":"article_comment","id":91045,"parentType":"article","parentId":6542,"uid":16955,"contents":"姨学作为一种立场并没有什么问题，这也是对于解决当前问题的一个角度的很好的思考和看法。支持姨学的同学可以采取多解释专用名词，详细说明等等方法来推广自己的论点，争取更多的支持者。不管是支持姨学还是不支持姨学，需要避免的是采取批评、诉诸人身、辱骂等方式引战，激起对立的情绪而不是论点。<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e3/Graham%27s_Hierarchy_of_Disagreement-zh-hans.svg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e3/Graham%27s_Hierarchy_of_Disagreement-zh-hans.svg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e3/Graham%27s_Hierarchy_of_Disagreement-zh-hans.svg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-10-26","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}